{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"alias":"brash-pisciform-loon","description":"## Why\nThe reconcile-bridge outage (bug 8002-a92f-0999-45dd) was caused by an *unparseable*\nworkflow: `f2bde8d3b5` put `${{ runner.temp }}` in a job-level `env:` of\n`reconcile-bridge.yml` (and its canary), a GitHub Actions startup failure that produced\nzero jobs for ~2 days. **CI never caught it** because `make lint` (the gate the `Verified`\nvote runs) scopes actionlint to `release.yml` ONLY — see `Makefile` (`RELEASE_WORKFLOW`,\ncomment: \"Scoped to release.yml — NOT repo-wide (F1/F3 harden other workflows separately)\").\nEvery other workflow, including the critical bridge + canary, is unvalidated, so an\ninvalid-workflow change merges with a green Verified vote and silently disables the workflow.\n\n## What\nExpand the CI actionlint (and consider zizmor) coverage from `release.yml` to **all**\n`.github/workflows/*.yml` / `*.yaml`, so the context-availability / parse-error class of bug\nis blocked at review time. Measured cost is ZERO today: `actionlint .github/workflows/*.yml\n.github/workflows/*.yaml` exits 0 with 0 findings after the 8002 fix, so no allowlist or\ncleanup is needed to turn the gate on.\n\n## Scope\n- `Makefile` lint target: lint all workflows (a new `ALL_WORKFLOWS`/glob), not just `RELEASE_WORKFLOW`.\n- Keep the macOS-leg skip / pinned-binary install logic as-is.\n- Confirm `test.yml` + `gerrit-verify.yaml` both run the widened `make lint` (parity — see\n  tests/unit/test_ci_workflow_parity.py) so the gate is enforced pre-merge, not only post-merge.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] `make lint` runs actionlint against every `.github/workflows/*.yml` and `*.yaml`, not just `release.yml`.\n- [ ] Reintroducing a `${{ runner.temp }}` job-level env (the 8002 defect) makes `make lint` FAIL.\n- [ ] `make lint` passes on the current tree (0 pre-existing actionlint findings across workflows).\n- [ ] The widened gate runs in BOTH the pre-merge (gerrit-verify.yaml) and post-merge (test.yml) legs.","id":"466f-9764-cd9c-450e","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Harden CI: extend actionlint coverage to ALL workflows (not just release.yml) — the gap that let the reconcile-bridge startup failure merge"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784232304564777001,"uuid":"d884e888-0ce5-4db5-8ac5-9cc5aafb94c1"}